00:01:31.410 --> 00:01:33.344
If you were a beatnik
jazz musician,

00:01:33.344 --> 00:01:34.760
you called it being
in the pocket.

00:01:34.760 --> 00:01:37.890
If you're a stand-up comic,
you call it the forever box.

00:01:37.890 --> 00:01:39.650
Flow is sort of
a technical term.

00:01:39.650 --> 00:01:42.081
And it is technically
defined as an optimal state

00:01:42.081 --> 00:01:43.830
of consciousness, a
state of consciousness

00:01:43.830 --> 00:01:47.390
where we perform our best
and we feel our best.

00:01:47.390 --> 00:01:51.290
It refers to those moments
of rapt attention and total

00:01:51.290 --> 00:01:54.667
absorption, where we get so
focused on the task at hand

00:01:54.667 --> 00:01:56.000
that everything else disappears.

00:01:56.000 --> 00:01:58.820
