00:40:42.530 --> 00:40:44.010
It's $10 trillion a year.

00:40:44.010 --> 00:40:46.550
One sixth of the
global economy is

00:40:46.550 --> 00:40:48.692
what we spend getting
out of our heads,

00:40:48.692 --> 00:40:49.900
and getting out of ourselves.

00:40:49.900 --> 00:40:50.370
That's what we spend.

00:40:50.370 --> 00:40:51.990
JASON SILVA: The
altered states economy.

00:40:51.990 --> 00:40:53.480
STEVEN KOTLER: The altered
