00:46:23.620 --> 00:46:24.890
is transient hypofrontality.

00:46:24.890 --> 00:46:27.490
So there's a part of your
brain, the right parietal lobe,

00:46:27.490 --> 00:46:31.030
that is what separate--
generates a barrier

00:46:31.030 --> 00:46:32.180
between self and others.

00:46:32.180 --> 00:46:35.040
So it exists so I can
walk around this room

00:46:35.040 --> 00:46:36.690
and not bump into furniture.

00:46:36.690 --> 00:46:38.265
So if I have a stroke
