00:46:44.270 --> 00:46:46.240
So during intense
concentration--

00:46:46.240 --> 00:46:47.970
like shows up in
meditation, or flow,

00:46:47.970 --> 00:46:50.220
or things like this-- part
of the brain shuts down.

00:46:50.220 --> 00:46:52.960
