separate self from other.

00:46:52.960 --> 00:46:55.342
And that point,
you're convinced--

00:46:55.342 --> 00:46:57.050
because there's no
other data available--

00:46:57.050 --> 00:46:58.620
that you are one
with everything.

00:46:58.620 --> 00:47:02.340
The same thing is going on if
you're using psilocybin or LSD.

00:47:02.340 --> 00:47:03.800
It's the same mechanism.

00:47:03.800 --> 00:47:05.020
All the roads lead to Rome.

00:47:05.020 --> 00:47:06.660
It doesn't matter
how you get in.

