00:48:44.550 --> 00:48:47.089
pattern and pre-configure
the input signals that

00:48:47.089 --> 00:48:48.880
were coming in when a
person is in a highly

00:48:48.880 --> 00:48:52.740
suggestible psychedelic state,
you could script the journey.

