00:58:18.170 --> 00:58:18.470
STEVEN KOTLER: Yeah.

00:58:18.470 --> 00:58:20.390
There's a chapter in
"Tomorrowland" on it.

00:58:20.390 --> 00:58:24.220
So earlier when I was talking
about knobs and levers

00:58:24.220 --> 00:58:29.190
in the brain-- I'm not saying
