00:58:33.080 --> 00:58:35.610
But just because
I can tell you how

00:58:35.610 --> 00:58:38.430
the neurobiology of
spiritual experience works,

00:58:38.430 --> 00:58:39.890
all that means is
these experiences

00:58:39.890 --> 00:58:40.973
are mediated in the brain.

00:58:40.973 --> 00:58:44.260
So if you're spiritually
inclined, if you're religious,

00:58:44.260 --> 00:58:47.380
what I'm talking about does
not disavow what you believe.

00:58:47.380 --> 00:58:50.230
It just says these experiences
are mediated through the brain.

00:58:50.230 --> 00:58:53.010
But we now know
that flow states,

00:58:53.010 --> 00:58:55.730
so-called mystical experiences,
psychedelic-- these

00:58:55.730 --> 00:58:57.950
are all the same
structures in the brain.

00:58:57.950 --> 00:59:02.550
And we're getting really good
at figuring out where they are,

00:59:02.550 --> 00:59:04.090
and how to precipitate them.

00:59:04.090 --> 00:59:06.370
Where I think that's
interesting is

00:59:06.370 --> 00:59:09.600
I think we're at the
very front edge of this.

00:59:09.600 --> 00:59:11.570
I think for years,
and years, and years,

00:59:11.570 --> 00:59:14.520
if you go by what the Buddhist
meditators have told us,

00:59:14.520 --> 00:59:16.480
that these things go
on and on forever.

00:59:16.480 --> 00:59:18.520
There's layer, after
layer, after layer.

00:59:18.520 --> 00:59:22.190
I think we're at the front
edge of decoding that stuff.

00:59:22.190 --> 00:59:24.214
I'm really interested
to what happens

00:59:24.214 --> 00:59:25.380
as we get deeper and deeper.

00:59:25.380 --> 00:59:27.390
Because there are weird
questions, even in flow.

00:59:27.390 --> 00:59:28.848
We were talking
about this earlier.

00:59:28.848 --> 00:59:31.850
You have access to really
