00:59:35.670 --> 00:59:38.480
10% of it doesn't make
any sense whatsoever.

00:59:38.480 --> 00:59:40.310
And it really feels magical.

00:59:40.310 --> 00:59:43.770
And there's not an easy
way to explain it away.

00:59:43.770 --> 00:59:45.567
I'd certainly love an
explanation for it.

00:59:45.567 --> 00:59:47.400
And I think poking
deeper into these realms,

00:59:47.400 --> 00:59:49.233
especially into the
science of these realms,

00:59:49.233 --> 00:59:50.660
